(b) Find \(C'(100)\). (What does this mean?) $BR
(c) Find the cost of manufacturing the \(101^{st}\) pair of jeans.

$PAR

(a) \(C'(x)=\)\{ans_rule(20)\} $BR 
(b) \(C'(100)=\)\{ans_rule(20)\} dollars/pair $BR
